My sister sent this to the family but I have to share. My niece Jennifer Locke Christopher a professional dancer (Hamilton, The Heights) dedicated this to my mom and later this was done at my mom’s memorial service. Yesterdays workout 7/12 with my daughter Shawn as well as weight work in the morning. Joined #adamgonners30daychallenge @adam_gonners. This is great motivation to do what I should be doing. #healthylifestyle #health #getmoving

So I missed yesterday helped out my oldest daughter, but to make up for it I did 2 workouts so I’m back on track. My daughter Shawn right along side me.  @adam_gonners accountability is helping. #fitnessjourney #healthylifestyle #consistencyiskey #adamgonners30daychallenge
My day 5 was a stretch and recovery day for back ache and old age lol. #adamgonners30daychallenge #healthylifestyle #health #keepmovingforward

Day 6 of #adamgooners30daychallenge, way to hot to walk in my neighborhood so chose to walk at the beach. Shoutout to @adam_gonners this has been great motivation. #healthylifestyle #health #exercisemotivation #exercisetherapy
Day 7 of #adamgonners30daychallenge quick walk to get it in.  #healthylifestyle #keepmoving
Day 8 of #adamgonners30daychallenge I’m happy that I’m sticking with it. #healthylifestyle #health #keepmoving
Day 9 -#adamgonners30daychallenge tried a new video for cardio, burned a few. #heathylifestyle #health ##keepitmoving
Day 10 of #adamgonners30daychallenge. Morning weight lifting and workout walking. Can’t wait to see what 30 days #healthylifestyle #health #pushthroughit
Day 11 #adamgonners30daychallenge 20 minute stretch was needed for tight muscles #healthy #healthylifestyle #flexibility
Day 12 #adamgonners30daychallenge turned some fun into exercise #health #healthylifestyle #keepmoving

Day 13 #adamgonners30daychallenge my daughter and I made up our own movements using our own music, then I did a standing abs video. Even if I don’t see it, I can’t get discouraged. There is more to bring healthy than looking thin. #health  #healthylifestyle #keepitmoving
Day 15, had to do a little make up for day 14.  Let’s get it #adamgonners30daychallenge half way there. #healthylifestyle #healthy #messup #thengetoverit
Day 16 of #adamgonners30daychallenge, #healthylifestyle #health #keepingitmoving

Day 17 of #adamgonners30daychallenge. My daughter and I did shoulders in the living room while running up and down steps between sets.  It was much harder minus air conditioning lol. #healthylifestyle #health #keepmoving still have to walk when it cools down 😎
Day 19 of #adamgonners30daychallenge walked while waiting for my car service, hot as hades with no trees. #healthylifestyle #health #keepmoving

Day 20 of #adamgonners30daychallenge the excuses I have always made, no time, can’t get to the gym, too hot outside sure became obsolete when fitness videos started on YouTube lol. HIIT workouts are no joke. Another big excuse was I can’t do that but Anni the former owner of my CrossFit gym always said keep moving and don’t compare yourself to 20 yr olds. Do what you can and modify to cover the rest. There was a lot of modifying but done ✅#healthylifestyle #health #keepmoving

Day 21 #adamgonners30daychallenge.  Working on getting my heart rate down quicker. Does anybody else struggle with that?  As a heart patient that’s really important to me. It’s not that my work outs are epic, it’s the accountability to the challenge that is keeping me consistent for now. I neglected my health for far too long. #healthylifestyle #health #keepitmoving #makeyourselfapriority

Day 22 of #adamgonners30daychallenge. End of the day and dragging almost didn’t get it in and then I saw @adam_gonners post at the gym, so I got off my butt and did this. #healthylifestyle #health #keepitmoving #noexcuses for 30 days at least lol

Day 23 of #adamgonners30daychallenge. I have found some pretty cool workouts on YouTube. Missed getting to the gym. This lady is really good, hard but you feel great when you go through it. My daughter did it like a champ. #healthylifestyle #health #keepmoving
Day #24 of #adamgonners30daychallenge. Made it to the gym for back and triceps. May do a online cardio video later, on a wait and see…..so hot 🔥🔥🔥🔥 #healthylifestyle #health #keepitmoving
Day 25 of #adamgonners30daychallenge strength training chest and biceps. Getting old sucks lol. #healthylifestyle #health #keepmoving #keepitmoving

Day 26 of #adamgonners30daychallenge.  First day in almost a month that I ate like crap. Waited way too late for intermittent fasting and when homemade tortilla chips and salsa were within reach I had to partake. I also had tacos which I haven’t had shells either. Really needed this workout my daughter and I did at the end of the day. Only 4 more days of my daily posts for accountability. I hope I can keep it up on my own. #healthylifestyle #health #keepitmoving.
Day 27 of #adamgonners30daychallenge 3 more days until completion.  My daughter and I did this quick 30 minute core. #healthylifestyle #health #keepitmoving

Day #28 of #adamgonners30daychallenge, when we decided to walk it was 73 degrees, that quickly changed into mid 80’s by the time we hit it together. My husband even joined me and my daughter on his recovery walk for part of the way. We had all these plans for more hills but the heat beat us down. The small breeze did not help lol. #healthylifestyle #health #keepmoving

If it sounds too good to be true, it’s probably not. These miracle #xtremefit Keto gummies are full of sugar and high fructose corn syrup. Maybe I’m wrong but I thought the whole Keto mantra was anti sugar. I guess I’m stuck doing this the old fashioned way of diet and exercise lol. #noeasywayout #putinthework #getwhatyoupayfor in sweat

Day 30 -#adamgonners30daychallenge, did not get a chance to complete day 29 but I will do it tomorrow. Did a walk at the marina with both my daughters @chef_kikis_kitchen and Shawn.  Had a goal to finish 5 miles walking in under 1.5 hours and I made it. #smallvictories Challenge has come to an end, thank you @adam_gonners  for the inspiration and push to get going on exercise, much appreciated. #healthylifestyle #health #keepmoving

Even when you want to do good things, you still sometimes have that feeling of you haven’t done enough. I love that my long time friend @steve.overton.520 posted this right in the middle of this season when people are spending way too much money for gifts as if the value takes away from the thought.  I used to volunteer for their family’s field hockey league. I never played but just seeing his beautiful family from his wife Lisa to his 2 sons and daughter working together and all that love gave me joy. I tried to never miss it.  These words are bringing me back to the reason for the season. Give with all your heart and the rest is there. We @maketheworld.a.betterplace will continue to try to make a difference and our little part may bring happiness to someone’s life. Happy Holidays, and Peace be with you .  #peace #love #givingheart

Born on this day 57 years ago was a beautiful baby girl who I had the fortune to have as my little sister-in-law.  She was a brilliant honors student in high school when we met. She had a style and a class all her own. Melanie introduced me to the music of Adam Ant, Ska, Rockabilly and Living Colour.  Not only was she smart, but she was really creative.  We had our own little business from her vision of making place mats, screens and hats decorated with Fabric from the Ivory Coast.  I miss her sass and her compassion. She was the first person to tell me the saying “Save a ho”, I laughed and laughed. She was a mother and loved her sons. With all that going on somehow she let someone and this world beat her down. I would always tell her you are so much more than that. Happy heavenly birthday Mel,  I love you and will miss you forever. ❤️❤️❤️❤️ #heavenlybirthday  #love #sisterhood
